    <!-- Quote Section -->
    <section class="quote-section">
      <div class="quote-header">
        <h1>
          <span id="star1">✨</span><span id="star2">✨</span><br />
          Users are experiencing greater happiness and stress-free living!
        </h1>
      </div>

      <div class="quote-cards">
        <div class="quote-card">
          <p class="quote-text">
            “Hobby Tribe is so delightful and engaging! Whether you're a casual
            gamer or someone looking to explore new hobbies in a fun and
            interactive way, this place offers something unique and refreshing.”
          </p>
          <p class="quote-author1">Regular user of the platform</p>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-card">
          <p class="quote-text">
            “By dancing my stress is reducing. It’s improving my mood,
            maintaining and building my strength; it’s reducing my depression
            and increasing my energy. I am thoroughly enjoying this dance tribe,
            thank you."
          </p>
          <p class="quote-author">User on learning a hobby to reduce stress</p>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-card">
          <p class="quote-text">
            “Hobby Tribe helps relieve my stress, anxiety. It provides multiple
            skill development learning solutions. The platform offers learning
            solutions on art & craft, computer science, creative writing, dance,
            chess, and more.”
          </p>
          <p class="quote-author">User on the benefits of using Hobby Tribe</p>
        </div>
      </div>
